messages.about.title: Welcome to the CollectionSpace Anthropology Demo
messages.about.contentHTML:
CollectionSpace is a free, open-source collections management application for museums, historical societies, natural science collections, and more.

This demo site is running the current version the anthropology profile of CollectionSpace, which includes fields and procedures useful for anthropology collections. If youâ€™re interested in a version of CollectionSpace configured to meet the needs of a different domain, please visit our demo landing page to view all available options. Examples include Botanical Garden, Fine Art, Herbarium, Local History & Material Culture, and Public Art.

To log in, use the email admin@anthro.collectionspace.org, with the case-sensitive password Administrator. To view in read-only mode, use the email reader@anthro.collectionspace.org with the password reader.

Not sure where to get started? Follow along with one of our quick-start guides:

  • Create a new object: PDF Screencast
  • Link to an image: PDF Screencast
  • Add a storage location: PDF Screencast

We rebuild this demo site weekly so don't worry, you won't break it!
